<section class="how-section">
  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <p class="lead">Simple. Personal. Lasting. Three steps to keep them close.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <h3>Choose Your Birthstone</h3>
      <p>Select from 12 genuine birthstone colors that represent your loved one's birth month or personality.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <h3>Fill with the Funnel Kit</h3>
      <p>Use the included free funnel kit to gently transfer a small portion of ashes into the pendant. Screw-top seals securely.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <h3>Wear Forever</h3>
      <p>Put it on. Keep them close to your heart. Rain or shine, this stainless steel necklace lasts a lifetime.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
